Title: 'Barcelona Aventura '
DateModified: '2019-03-12'
DatePublished: '2019-03-12'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/barcelona-aventura
SetInCountry: Spain
Category: I didn't expect to find
AuthorName: Suzanne  Vachula
AuthorCountry: United States of America
Text: "I was study at the Universite Paris 1 Pantheon-Sorbonne Faculte de Droit during\
  \ the Spring of 2018.  I took a vacation to Spain during my Spring Break. It was\
  \ a wonderful trip and I enjoyed the beach,  but I was met with a few things I hadn't\
  \ expected. \nFirst, I thought it'd be warm in Spain during that time of year. I\
  \ was wrong. I only brought shorts and skirts and one pair of pants. I walked around\
  \ the city a ton during my first day to the point that I chaffed through my pants\
  \ and my inner thighs were a sore mess. Naturally that happened the first day. I\
  \ didn't expect to find myself in horrible pain from a chaffing incident. I ran\
  \ down to a Zara down the street from my hostel and got a new pair off pants,  but\
  \ I spent the rest of the trip hobbling around like a weirdo. It didn't stop me\
  \ from my aventura!\nSecond,  I spent my whole trip in the same hostel, but because\
  \ of scheduling I ended up staying in several different rooms during my stay. My\
  \ first room: lovely,  all girls,  smelled as nice as a hostel can smell. My second\
  \ room... I didn't expect to find a Spanish couple making out on my bed!  I was\
  \ unfortunately placed in a co-ed room with like 10 Spaniards traveling as a group.\
  \ That was a mistake. I came back to the hostel after a long day of walking around\
  \ the city to find this couple in my bed. They apologized and I just asked them\
  \ not to be there when I got back and I went for another walk. It's all part of\
  \ the aventura right?  I went to the Sea once again and enjoyed the slightly misting\
  \ weather. It was in my third room when I realized that I'm aging quickly as late\
  \ teen/ealy twenty somethings.. Mind you, I'm 23..pregamed and headed out for the\
  \ night while I enjoyed the peace of moving back into an all girls room."
